profile:
Cottage country has always been my escape from the big city. I grew up in Lorne park and spent the summers at my family cottage working in Parry Sound. I decide to make it my home. I got my Carpentry license through a local builder and decided to go out and start my own company. Been in the trade for 10 years and now my own company for 4 successful years. With many happy clients and amazing projects. Let me turn your dreams in to your reality.

Owner, operator
name: Grant M. Towers Custom Carpentry

profile: W.S. Morgan Construction Limited is Premier Builder / General Contractor of choice to Parry Sound & Muskoka for over 35 years.
